{"word":"ἐπιβάλλω","slug":"ἐπιβάλλω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ἐπιβάλλω</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἐπί\">ἐπί</a>, <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:βάλλω\">βάλλω</a></el>]<b><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>1.</pp></b> ‘move <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ someth.\">someth.</a> so as to put it over/on’ <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ someth.\">someth.</a>, <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ tr.\">tr.</a> <b>put on, lay on <a href='B:470 9:16'>Mt 9:16</a>; <a href='B:480 11:7'>Mk 11:7</a>; <a href='B:490 9:62'>Lk 9:62</a>; <a href='B:730 18:19'>Rv 18:19</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ v.l.\">v.l.</a></b> Freq. with suggestion of violence, <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:χείρ\">χείρ</a></el> <b><a href='B:470 26:50'>Mt 26:50</a>; <a href='B:480 14:46'>Mk 14:46</a>; <a href='B:490 20:19'>Lk 20:19</a>; <a href='B:500 7:30'>J 7:30</a>; <a href='B:510 4:3'>Ac 4:3</a>;</b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ cp.\">cp.</a> <b><a href='B:530 7:35'>1 Cor 7:35</a>.<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>2.</pp></b> ‘move forcefully against’, <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ intr.\">intr.</a> <b>dash against <a href='B:480 4:37'>Mk 4:37</a>.</b> Some violent gesture of lamentation is <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ prob.\">prob.</a> implied <b><a href='B:480 14:72'>14:72</a></b> (<el>ἐπιβαλὼν ἔϰλαιεν</el> he broke into tears). <b><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>3.</pp></b> ‘be appropriate in the order of events’, <b>fall to, belong to <a href='B:490 15:12'>Lk 15:12</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ἐπιβαίνω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ἐπιβαλῶ\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}